Subject: [PATCH] 8993: Annotations: Local variable handler

Two possible forms are supported:
	{@local <func_sym> <var_sym>}
and
	{@local <func_sym> <hash_marker> <var_hash>}

The <hash_marker> can be any string that starts with a space
e.g. " USER" or " AUTO". Quotes are required.
